NOTICE: This repository intentionally contains cryptographic private keys
(under keys-home/), published on purpose as public test fixtures for the
Swamp testnet "Puddle". They provide no access to any production system,
protect nothing, and must never be reused outside this dataset. Anything
signed with these keys is test material by definition: every envelope in
this testnet carries the header `Testnet: yes`, and the keys' DIDs are
rostered in world/manifest.json so real-pond readers can filter them.

If a secret scanner sent you here: this is the rare true positive that is
also a false alarm. See README.md, "The testnet convention."
